                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Policeman, B</hi> 234). I took the prisoner in custody on the night of 31st May—I searched him, and found on him 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 3<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. and a knife, I told him the charge—he denied it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I am quite innocent—I went to this house to my dinner, and went away to my master's, and before I got there I was taken by the policeman—I am a stranger here.</p>
